  max: 100,
  standardHeaders: true,
  legacyHeaders: false,
});
app.use(limiter);
```

#### 5. No Request Body Parsing or Size Limits
There's no body parser, and if one is added later, there's no size cap — which can enable memory exhaustion attacks:

```js
