app.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Server running on port ${PORT}`));
```

#### 7. No CORS Policy
No explicit CORS configuration means browser behavior is undefined. Restrict origins explicitly using [`cors`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/cors):

```js
const cors = require('cors');
app.use(cors({
  origin: process.env.ALLOWED_ORIGIN || 'https://yourdomain.com',
  methods: ['GET'],
}));
```

#### 8. No Request Logging
No request logging makes security auditing and incident response difficult. Use [`morgan`](https://www.npmjs.com/package/morgan) or a structured logger:

